<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net" agent="Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/143.0.0.0" version="29.2.9" scale="1" border="0"> <diagram name="Page-1" id="SQov-SjmR0krn36qHSMv"> <mxGraphModel dx="5880" dy="-128" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0"> <root> <mxCell id="0" /> <mxCell id="1" parent="0" /> <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{"data":"@startuml
' =========================
' GLOBAL STYLE
' =========================
skinparam backgroundColor #0b0f14
skinparam defaultFontColor #e5e7eb
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam linetype ortho

skinparam package {
 BackgroundColor #020617
 BorderColor #64748b
 FontColor #e5e7eb
}

skinparam node {
 BackgroundColor #111827
 BorderColor #6b7280
 FontColor #e5e7eb
}

skinparam cloud {
 BackgroundColor #020617
 BorderColor #9ca3af
 FontColor #e5e7eb
}

skinparam ArrowColor #9ca3af

title <b>Network Topology</b>

' =========================
' EDGE / CORE
' =========================
cloud \"Internet\" as internet
node \"UDM Pro\nFirewall | NAT | VPN\nDNS Override\" as udm #1f2937
node \"USW-24\nCore Switch\" as usw #020617

internet -down-> udm
udm -down-> usw

' =========================
' VLAN 10 – MANAGEMENT (TRUSTED)
' =========================
package \"VLAN 10 – Management (Trusted)\" #0f172a {
 together {
 node \"Pi-hole Primary\" as pihole1 #064e3b
 node \"Pi-hole Secondary\" as pihole2 #064e3b
 node \"Grafana + Prometheus\" as grafana #065f46
 }

 together {
 node \"Proxmox VE\" as pve #065f46
 node \"CA Server\" as ca #065f46
 node \"Ansible Control Node\nSemaphore\" as ansible #065f46
 node \"Nginx Proxy Manager\" as npm #065f46
 }
}

usw -down-> pihole1
usw -down-> pve

' =========================
' VLAN 15 – BACKUP (TRUSTED)
' =========================
package \"VLAN 15 – Backup (Trusted)\" #0f172a {
 together {
 node \"Proxmox Backup Server\" as pbs #064e3b
 node \"OpenMediaVault\" as omv #064e3b
 }
}

pve -down-> pbs

' =========================
' VLAN 30 – APPLICATION SERVERS (TRUSTED)
' =========================
package \"VLAN 30 – Application Servers (Trusted)\" #020617 {
 node \"BookStack\" as bookstack #065f46
}

pbs -down-> bookstack

' =========================
' TRUST BOUNDARY (DIVIDER NODE – SAFE)
' =========================
node \"TRUST BOUNDARY\" as trust_boundary #0b1220

bookstack -down-> trust_boundary

' =========================
' VLAN 75 – GUEST (ISOLATED)
' =========================
package \"VLAN 75 – Guest (Isolated)\" #111827 {
 node \"Guest Clients\nInternet Only\" as guest #7f1d1d
}

trust_boundary -down-> guest

' =========================
' VLAN 50 – IOT (LOW TRUST)
' =========================
package \"VLAN 50 – IoT (Low Trust)\" #111827 {
 node \"IoT Devices\" as iot #7c2d12
}

guest -down-> iot

' =========================
' VLAN 25 – MEDIA (LOW TRUST)
' =========================
package \"VLAN 25 – Media (Low Trust)\" #111827 {
 node \"Media Devices\" as media #7c2d12
}

iot -down-> media

' =========================
' CONTROL PLANE FLOWS
' =========================
pihole1 <--> pihole2 : DNS Sync

ansible -[#22c55e,dashed]-> pve : Automation
ansible -[#22c55e,dashed]-> pbs : Automation
ansible -[#22c55e,dashed]-> omv : Automation

' =========================
' DATA PLANE FLOWS
' =========================
pve -[#38bdf8]-> pbs : VM Backups

npm -[#60a5fa]-> bookstack : HTTPS
npm -[#60a5fa]-> grafana : HTTPS
npm -[#60a5fa]-> pihole1 : HTTPS
npm -[#60a5fa]-> pve : HTTPS
npm -[#60a5fa]-> pbs : HTTPS
npm -[#60a5fa]-> omv : HTTPS

@enduml
